## Background

{{Description|"Why, [Berath](/berath/) smiles upon you! What fortune, that on this turn upon the Wheel, you should find yourself before the finest merchant in all the Deadfire!"}}
This mysterious merchant appears in [Port Maje Harbor](/portMajeHarbor/), on the western wall of the market.

